News.Title: Rajputana Industries Reports Strong Sales Growth in FY 2024-25
News.Summary: Rajputana Industries has announced a significant year-over-year sales growth of 69.4% for the fiscal year 2024-25, with sales reaching Rs 553 crore.

News.Title: Rajputana Industries Reports Significant Sales Growth
News.Summary: Rajputana Industries has announced a substantial increase in its provisional sales figures. The company achieved sales of ₹403.34 crore, compared to ₹217 crore in the previous comparable period, representing a significant growth in revenue.
